<p>I am using URL scope in <code>application.cfc</code></p>  <pre><code>&lt;cfset structAppend(url,createObject("component", "com.thr.threads"))&gt; </code></pre>  <p>It is working fine but when I set <code>accessors</code> and define <code>cfproperty</code>:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;cfproperty name="accid"  type="string" default="#application.conf.accId#"&gt; </code></pre>  <p>the <code>#application.conf.accId</code>  variable starts giving error. Normally it works fine.</p>  <ol> <li>How to define global functions in ColdFusion?</li> <li>How to pass an object reference in ColdFusion?</li> </ol>